prompts.frontCover: A whimsical, flat 2D botanical illustration featuring a charming, cartoon-style sloth hanging upside down from a lush, leafy branch overflowing with detailed, colorful hibiscus and bird-of-paradise flowers. The sloth is smiling dreamily, wearing a tiny, festive party hat askew on its head. In the center of the design, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Let's get wild... or, you know, just hang out." The overall composition is a soft, organic shape, framed by elegant floral and leafy elements against a clean, light background.
